{% comment %}
  CUSTOM · Acquista — homepage buy box

  Sezione custom homepage (pattern: .claude/patterns/building-custom-homepage-section.md).
  Buy box modellato sulla LP B2C (lp-offerta) ma sobrio e allineato a Dawn:
  usa i token del tema. L'add to cart usa lo snippet ufficiale Dawn `buy-buttons`
  (<product-form> + product-form.js), come featured-product. Vedi decision 006.

  Interattivita' (selezione variante, carousel) in assets/custom-buy-box.js, che
  aggiorna l'input name="id" del form al cambio variante.
{% endcomment %}

{{ 'custom-buy-box.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

{%- liquid
  assign product = section.settings.product
-%}

{%- if product == blank -%}
  {%- comment -%} Editor: nessun prodotto scelto. Placeholder minimo. {%- endcomment -%}
  <div class="custom-buy-box custom-buy-box--empty">
    <p>Seleziona un prodotto nelle impostazioni della sezione.</p>
  </div>
{%- else -%}
  {%- liquid
    assign first_variant = product.selected_or_first_available_variant
    assign product_form_id = 'custom-buy-box-form-' | append: section.id

    # Rileva quale opzione e' il colore e quale la taglia, per nome (come lp-offerta).
    # Il match per nome rende la sezione indipendente dall'ordine delle opzioni.
    assign color_option = null
    assign size_option = null
    for opt in product.options_with_values
      assign oname = opt.name | downcase
      if oname contains 'color' or oname contains 'colore' or oname contains 'colour'
        assign color_option = opt
      elsif oname contains 'taglia' or oname contains 'size' or oname contains 'misura'
        assign size_option = opt
      endif
    endfor
    # Fallback taglia: prima opzione diversa dal colore.
    if size_option == null
      for opt in product.options_with_values
        if color_option == null or opt.position != color_option.position
          assign size_option = opt
          break
        endif
      endfor
    endif

    assign featured_media = first_variant.featured_media | default: product.featured_media
    assign image_media = product.media | where: 'media_type', 'image'
  -%}

  {%- comment -%} id="acquista": ancora per link interni (es. #acquista). {%- endcomment -%}
  <custom-buy-box id="acquista" class="custom-buy-box color-{{ section.settings.color_scheme }}">

    {%- comment -%} Dati varianti Liquid -> JS (pattern blob, niente interpolazione). {%- endcomment -%}
    <script type="application/json" class="custom-buy-box__data">
      {{ product.variants | json }}
    </script>

    {%- comment -%}
      Mappa variante -> media id della sua galleria colore (metafield
      custom.variant_gallery, stesso meccanismo di lp-offerta). Il file della
      galleria si lega al media del prodotto confrontando l'src.
    {%- endcomment -%}
    <script type="application/json" class="custom-buy-box__vg">
      {
        {%- for variant in product.variants -%}
          {%- unless forloop.first -%},{%- endunless -%}
          "{{ variant.id }}": [
            {%- assign vg_files = variant.metafields.custom.variant_gallery.value -%}
            {%- if vg_files != blank -%}
              {%- assign first_hit = true -%}
              {%- for vg_file in vg_files -%}
                {%- for media in product.media -%}
                  {%- if vg_file.image.src == media.src -%}
                    {%- unless first_hit -%},{%- endunless -%}{{ media.id }}
                    {%- assign first_hit = false -%}
                  {%- endif -%}
                {%- endfor -%}
              {%- endfor -%}
            {%- endif -%}
          ]
        {%- endfor -%}
      }
    </script>

    <div class="custom-buy-box__inner">

      {%- comment -%}
        ============ COLONNA MEDIA ============
        Carousel scroll-snap: swipe nativo su mobile. Dots di navigazione su
        tutti i viewport (generati da JS), uno per slide visibile.
      {%- endcomment -%}
      <div class="custom-buy-box__media">
        <div class="custom-buy-box__slides" data-slides>
          {%- if image_media.size > 0 -%}
            {%- for media in image_media -%}
              <img
                class="custom-buy-box__slide"
                data-media-id="{{ media.id }}"
                src="{{ media | image_url: width: 800 }}"
                alt="{{ media.alt | default: product.title | escape }}"
                width="{{ media.preview_image.width }}"
                height="{{ media.preview_image.height }}"
                loading="lazy"
              >
            {%- endfor -%}
          {%- elsif featured_media -%}
            <img
              class="custom-buy-box__slide"
              data-media-id="{{ featured_media.id }}"
              src="{{ featured_media | image_url: width: 800 }}"
              alt="{{ featured_media.alt | default: product.title | escape }}"
              width="{{ featured_media.preview_image.width }}"
              height="{{ featured_media.preview_image.height }}"
              loading="lazy"
            >
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>

        {%- comment -%} Dots: navigazione carousel su tutti i viewport, generati da JS (uno per slide visibile). {%- endcomment -%}
        <div class="custom-buy-box__dots" data-dots></div>
      </div>

      {%- comment -%} ============ COLONNA INFO ============ {%- endcomment -%}
      <div class="custom-buy-box__info">

        <h2 class="custom-buy-box__title">{{ product.title | escape }}</h2>

        {%- comment -%} Recensioni fake, come la LP: 5 stelle piene + testo editabile. {%- endcomment -%}
        <div class="custom-buy-box__reviews">
          <span class="custom-buy-box__stars" aria-hidden="true">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</span>
          <span class="custom-buy-box__reviews-text">{{ section.settings.reviews_text | escape }}</span>
        </div>

        {%- comment -%} Prezzo + rata raggruppati: gap stretto fra loro. {%- endcomment -%}
        <div class="custom-buy-box__price-block">
          <div class="custom-buy-box__price">
            <span class="custom-buy-box__price-current" data-price>{{ first_variant.price | money }}</span>
            <s
              class="custom-buy-box__price-compare"
              data-compare
              {% unless first_variant.compare_at_price > first_variant.price %}hidden{% endunless %}
            >{{ first_variant.compare_at_price | money }}</s>
          </div>

          {%- comment -%} Importo rata dinamico = prezzo variante / 3. Frase hardcoded. {%- endcomment -%}
          <p class="custom-buy-box__installment">
            Oppure <strong>3 rate da <span data-installment>{{ first_variant.price | divided_by: 3 | money }}</span></strong> con Klarna o PayPal
          </p>
        </div>

        {%- if color_option -%}
          <div class="custom-buy-box__opt" data-color-opt data-pos="{{ color_option.position | minus: 1 }}">
            <p class="custom-buy-box__opt-label">
              {{ color_option.name | escape }}: <span data-color-value>{{ color_option.selected_value | escape }}</span>
            </p>
            <div class="custom-buy-box__swatches">
              {%- for value in color_option.values -%}
                {%- comment -%}
                  Sfondo swatch: swatch Shopify se configurato, altrimenti fallback
                  per i colori noti del prodotto (lo store non ha sempre gli swatch).
                {%- endcomment -%}
                {%- capture sw_style -%}
                  {%- if value.swatch.color -%}--swatch:{{ value.swatch.color }};
                  {%- elsif value.swatch.image -%}--swatch:url({{ value.swatch.image | image_url: width: 120 }});
                  {%- else -%}
                    {%- assign vname = value | downcase -%}
                    {%- if vname contains 'nero' or vname contains 'black' -%}--swatch:#1a1a1a;
                    {%- elsif vname contains 'testa di moro' -%}--swatch:#3d1a0a;
                    {%- elsif vname contains 'marrone' or vname contains 'brown' -%}--swatch:#5c3317;
                    {%- else -%}--swatch:#d9d9d9;
                    {%- endif -%}
                  {%- endif -%}
                {%- endcapture -%}
                <button
                  type="button"
                  class="custom-buy-box__swatch{% if value.selected %} is-on{% endif %}"
                  data-swatch
                  data-value="{{ value | escape }}"
                  title="{{ value | escape }}"
                  aria-label="{{ value | escape }}"
                  style="{{ sw_style | strip_newlines | strip }}"
                ></button>
              {%- endfor -%}
            </div>
          </div>
        {%- endif -%}

        {%- if size_option -%}
          <div class="custom-buy-box__opt" data-size-opt data-pos="{{ size_option.position | minus: 1 }}">
            <p class="custom-buy-box__opt-label">
              {{ size_option.name | escape }}: <span data-size-value>{{ size_option.selected_value | escape }}</span>
            </p>
            <div class="custom-buy-box__pills">
              {%- for value in size_option.values -%}
                <button
                  type="button"
                  class="custom-buy-box__pill{% if value.selected %} is-on{% endif %}"
                  data-pill
                  data-value="{{ value | escape }}"
                >{{ value | escape }}</button>
              {%- endfor -%}
            </div>
          </div>
        {%- endif -%}

        {%- comment -%}
          Bottoni che aprono i due <dialog> (guida taglie / schede tecniche).
          data-open-dialog combacia con data-dialog sul <dialog>; logica in custom-buy-box.js.
        {%- endcomment -%}
        <div class="custom-buy-box__info-btns">
          <button type="button" class="custom-buy-box__info-btn" data-open-dialog="size">
            {%- comment -%} icona righello {%- endcomment -%}
            <svg class="custom-buy-box__info-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
              <path d="M21.3 15.3 8.7 2.7a1 1 0 0 0-1.4 0L2.7 7.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l12.6 12.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l4.6-4.6a1 1 0 0 0 0-1.4Z"/>
              <path d="m7.5 10.5 2 2M11 7l2 2M14.5 3.5l2 2M4 14l2 2"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Guida taglie</span>
          </button>
          <button type="button" class="custom-buy-box__info-btn" data-open-dialog="specs">
            {%- comment -%} icona documento {%- endcomment -%}
            <svg class="custom-buy-box__info-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
              <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8Z"/>
              <path d="M14 2v6h6M8 13h8M8 17h8M8 9h2"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Schede tecniche</span>
          </button>
        </div>

        {%- comment -%}
          Add to cart — snippet ufficiale Dawn `buy-buttons` (stesso usato da
          featured-product): <product-form> + {% form 'product' %} + product-form.js.
          custom-buy-box.js aggiorna l'input name="id" al cambio variante.
        {%- endcomment -%}
        {%- render 'buy-buttons',
          product: product,
          product_form_id: product_form_id,
          section_id: section.id
        -%}

      </div>
    </div>

    {%- comment -%}
      Sticky CTA: barra nera in basso con bottone, scivola su dopo 200px di scroll
      e si nasconde quando questa sezione (#acquista) e' in viewport.
      Logica in custom-buy-box.js. data-sticky-cta sulla barra (e' lei a slidare).
    {%- endcomment -%}
    <div class="custom-buy-box__sticky-bar" data-sticky-cta>
      <a
        href="#acquista"
        class="custom-buy-box__sticky-cta button button--primary"
      >
        {{ section.settings.sticky_cta_label | escape }}
      </a>
    </div>

    {%- comment -%}
      Popup nativi <dialog> (top layer: niente conflitti z-index con sticky CTA/cart drawer).
      Contenuto hardcoded, portato 1:1 dal vecchio tema Horizon (home-buy-section.liquid).
      Apertura/chiusura in custom-buy-box.js. data-dialog combacia con data-open-dialog.
    {%- endcomment -%}
    <dialog
      id="cbb-dialog-size-{{ section.id }}"
      class="custom-buy-box__dialog"
      data-dialog="size"
      aria-labelledby="cbb-dialog-size-title-{{ section.id }}"
    >
      <div class="custom-buy-box__dialog-box">
        <button type="button" class="custom-buy-box__dialog-x" data-close-dialog aria-label="Chiudi">&times;</button>
        <h3 class="custom-buy-box__dialog-title" id="cbb-dialog-size-title-{{ section.id }}">Guida alla Taglia</h3>
        <div class="custom-buy-box__dialog-body">
          <p>Misura la lunghezza interna della soletta e confronta con la tabella.</p>
          <table class="custom-buy-box__stbl">
            <thead><tr><th>IT</th><th>Cm Soletta Interna</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>37</td><td>24,5 cm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>38</td><td>25 cm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>39</td><td>25,5 cm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>40</td><td>26,5 cm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>41</td><td>27,5 cm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>42</td><td>28 cm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>43</td><td>28,5 cm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>44</td><td>29 cm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>45</td><td>30 cm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>46</td><td>30,5 cm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>47</td><td>31 cm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>48</td><td>32 cm</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </dialog>

    <dialog
      id="cbb-dialog-specs-{{ section.id }}"
      class="custom-buy-box__dialog"
      data-dialog="specs"
      aria-labelledby="cbb-dialog-specs-title-{{ section.id }}"
    >
      <div class="custom-buy-box__dialog-box">
        <button type="button" class="custom-buy-box__dialog-x" data-close-dialog aria-label="Chiudi">&times;</button>
        <h3 class="custom-buy-box__dialog-title" id="cbb-dialog-specs-title-{{ section.id }}">Documentazione Tecnica</h3>
        <div class="custom-buy-box__dialog-body">
          <div class="custom-buy-box__doc-section">
            <p class="custom-buy-box__doc-label">Documenti comuni</p>
            <a class="custom-buy-box__doc-row" href="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0960/9527/3303/files/DPI-DRKAMPES-CERTIFICAZIONE-S3S.pdf?v=1776677825" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              <span class="custom-buy-box__doc-icon">&#8595;</span>
              <span class="custom-buy-box__doc-name">Certificazione DPI S3S</span>
              <span class="custom-buy-box__doc-type">PDF</span>
            </a>
            <a class="custom-buy-box__doc-row" href="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0960/9527/3303/files/NOTA-INFORMATIVA-DRKAMPES.pdf?v=1776677825" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              <span class="custom-buy-box__doc-icon">&#8595;</span>
              <span class="custom-buy-box__doc-name">Nota informativa</span>
              <span class="custom-buy-box__doc-type">PDF</span>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="custom-buy-box__doc-section">
            <p class="custom-buy-box__doc-label">Schede tecniche per modello</p>
            <a class="custom-buy-box__doc-row" href="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0960/9527/3303/files/DR_KAMPES_-_SCHEDA_TECNICA-20260420-BLACK.pdf?v=1776677825" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              <span class="custom-buy-box__doc-icon">&#8595;</span>
              <span class="custom-buy-box__doc-name">Dr Kampes Nere</span>
              <span class="custom-buy-box__doc-type">PDF</span>
            </a>
            <a class="custom-buy-box__doc-row" href="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0960/9527/3303/files/DR_KAMPES_-_SCHEDA_TECNICA-20260420-BLACK.pdf?v=1776677825" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              <span class="custom-buy-box__doc-icon">&#8595;</span>
              <span class="custom-buy-box__doc-name">Dr Kampes Testa di Moro</span>
              <span class="custom-buy-box__doc-type">PDF</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </dialog>

  </custom-buy-box>

  {%- comment -%} product-form.js: stesso caricamento di featured-product (guarded). {%- endcomment -%}
  <script src="{{ 'product-form.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>
  <script src="{{ 'custom-buy-box.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>
{%- endif -%}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "CUSTOM · Acquista",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "custom-buy-box-section",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "product",
      "id": "product",
      "label": "Prodotto"
    },
    {
      "type": "color_scheme",
      "id": "color_scheme",
      "label": "Schema colore",
      "default": "scheme-1"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "reviews_text",
      "label": "Testo recensioni",
      "default": "1200+ camionisti soddisfatti"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "sticky_cta_label",
      "label": "Testo bottone flottante",
      "default": "Acquista Ora"
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    { "name": "CUSTOM · Acquista" }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
